log() { echo "$@" >/dev/stderr }
p="$alfred_workflow_data/searches/$search.json"
log '.' log '/-------- REVEAL -------\' log "uid=$search" log "p=$p" log '\-------- REVEAL -------/'
echo -n "$p"
on run argv set thePath to item 1 of argv set posixFile to POSIX file thePath tell application "Finder" move posixFile to trash end tell end run
Import a search from a URL

query="$1"
log() { echo "$@" >&2 }
fatal() { echo -n "$@" log "$@" exit 1 }
log "." log "/---------- NEW ----------\\" log "query=$query"
log "engine=$engine" log "uid=$uid" log "title=$title" log "keyword=$keyword" log "pcencode=$pcencode" log "search_url=$search_url" log "suggest_url=$suggest_url"
log "icon=$icon"
opts=(add --env)
test -n "$title" || fatal 'required var "title" unset' test -n "$keyword" || fatal 'required var "keyword" unset' test -n "$search_url" || fatal 'required var "search_url" unset'
output="$( ./searchio $opts 2>&1 )" ok=$?
[[ $ok -ne 0 ]] && { log "$output" echo -n "$output" }
log "\\---------- NEW ----------/"
exit $ok
